      "TW": ""
    }
  },
  "Today is the routine inspection of the 014 Base's drainage system.": {
    "translation": "",
    "MultiLang": {
      "US": "",
      "JP": "",
      "CN": "",
      "KR": "",
      "TW": ""
    }
  },
  "According to the manual requirements, we need to descend from the platform industrial elevator and adjust the stability of the deep drainage device.": {
    "translation": "",
    "MultiLang": {
      "US": "",
      "JP": "",
      "CN": "",
      "KR": "",
      "TW": ""
    }
  },
  "Understand? Let's go.": {
    "translation": "",
    "MultiLang": {
      "US": "",
      "JP": "",
      "CN": "",
      "KR": "",
      "TW": ""
    }
  },
  ">> The elevator doors will close in 15s <<": {
    "translation": "",
    "MultiLang": {
      "US": "",
      "JP": "",
      "CN": "",
      "KR": "",
      "TW": ""
    }
  },
  "Hurry!": {
    "translation": "",
    "MultiLang": {
      "US": "",
      "JP": "",
      "CN": "",
      "KR": "",
      "TW": ""
    }
  },
  "There seems to be some strange noise overhead...": {
    "translation": "",
    "MultiLang": {
      "US": "",
      "JP": "",
      "CN": "",
      "KR": "",
      "TW": ""
    }
  },
  "Something is falling down!": {
