    "translation": "",
    "MultiLang": {
      "US": "",
      "JP": "",
      "CN": "",
      "KR": "",
      "TW": ""
    }
  },
  "The depth gauge shows that we are still 8,000 units from the ascent platform.": {
    "translation": "",
    "MultiLang": {
      "US": "",
      "JP": "",
      "CN": "",
      "KR": "",
      "TW": ""
    }
  },
  "Just hold on...": {
    "translation": "",
    "MultiLang": {
      "US": "",
      "JP": "",
      "CN": "",
      "KR": "",
      "TW": ""
    }
  },
  "Our soilders vanished like snowflakes...": {
    "translation": "",
    "MultiLang": {
      "US": "",
      "JP": "",
      "CN": "",
      "KR": "",
      "TW": ""
    }
  },
  "But the zombies came flooding in like a torrent!": {
    "translation": "",
    "MultiLang": {
      "US": "",
      "JP": "",
      "CN": "",
      "KR": "",
      "TW": ""
    }
  },
  "If I remember correctly, there are roads on both sides.": {
    "translation": "",
    "MultiLang": {
      "US": "",
      "JP": "",
      "CN": "",
      "KR": "",
      "TW": ""
    }
  },
  "To some extent, this is completely a trap ...": {
    "translation": "",
    "MultiLang": {
      "US": "",
      "JP": "",
      "CN": "",
      "KR": "",
      "TW": ""
    }
  },
  "I'm sorry, rookies, you didn't have to be caught up in this incident.": {
    "translation": "",
    "MultiLang": {
      "US": "",
      "JP": "",
      "CN": "",
      "KR": "",
      "TW": ""
    }
  },
  "The final destination is within our reach.": {
    "translation": "",
    "MultiLang": {
      "US": "",
      "JP": "",
      "CN": "",
      "KR": "",
      "TW": ""
    }
  },
  "I seem to already be able to see the sunlight on the ascent platform.": {
    "translation": "",
    "MultiLang": {
      "US": "",
      "JP": "",
      "CN": "",
      "KR": "",
      "TW": ""
    }
  },
  "Huff, all blast-resistant gates unlocked.": {
    "translation": "",
    "MultiLang": {
      "US": "",
      "JP": "",
      "CN": "",
      "KR": "",
      "TW": ""
    }
  },
  "My amigo, I am no longer useful, and the road ahead is for you to go, I'm gonna restart the power system of the ascent platform here.": {
    "translation": "",
    "MultiLang": {
      "US": "",
      "JP": "",
      "CN": "",
      "KR": "",
      "TW": ""
    }
  },
  "That golden platform, see it? I will stay here to cover the rear.": {
    "translation": "",
    "MultiLang": {
      "US": "",
      "JP": "",
      "CN": "",
      "KR": "",
      "TW": ""
    }
  },
  "As my prayer for our departed fellows.": {
    "translation": "",
    "MultiLang": {
      "US": "",
